These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, librarian
There are 2 different nationalities: french, spanish
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, ship
1. the librarian is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the pilot is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | cola    |
| Job           | librarian | pilot |
| Nationality   | french       | spanish  |
| Transport     | helicopter      | ship     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, country
2 different pets are kept: dog, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | kiwi | grapefruit |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | country         |
| Pet           | snake     | dog         |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, police-officer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, trance
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike
1. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking          | baking |
| Job           | police-officer | dancer     |
| Music-Genre   | house            | trance         |
| Transport     | bike         | jet-ski   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, scientific
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, soul
2 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig
1. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
2. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | coffee     | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | soul |
| Pet           | lizard | guinea-pig    |

