.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, broccoli
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, pop
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person eating cabbage is the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of blues is the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | almond-milk |
| Food          | broccoli   | cabbage |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | blues     |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile     |

 